꾆 2. Download and Run Jenkins
Download .war file from Jenkins run it on browser it will directly download
https://get.jenkins.io/war-stable/latest/jenkins.war
(save the above file (jenkins.war) path to a folder in C drive in Jenkins folder)
Move it to:
C:\Jenkins
Run Jenkins:
cd C:\Jenkins
java -jar jenkins.war --webroot=C:\Jenkins\temp
